<body class="bg-gray-100">

    <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-8">
      
      <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center text-center px-6 py-8 w-full">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800">About Hostel XO</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl">
          At Hostel XO, we are dedicated to providing a comfortable, welcoming, and affordable place for travelers from all over the world. Our mission is to create a community where guests can connect, share experiences, and create memories.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 w-full">
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-7/12 mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
              Our vision is to be the preferred hostel for travelers seeking a unique and memorable stay. We strive to achieve this by offering exceptional service, clean and stylish accommodations, and fostering a friendly and inclusive environment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-7/12 mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Prime locations in the heart of the city</li>
              <li>Comfortable and modern rooms</li>
              <li>Friendly and helpful staff</li>
              <li>Affordable rates</li>
              <li>Free Wi-Fi and breakfast</li>
              <li>A vibrant community of travelers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-7/12 mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
              Founded in 2022, Hostel XO was born from a passion for travel and a desire to create a space where travelers can feel at home. Our founders, avid travelers themselves, saw a need for affordable yet stylish accommodations and decided to turn their vision into reality.
            </p>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595599512948-b9831e5fc11c?q=80&w=2071&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Hostel Story" class="mt-4 w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-7/12 rounded-lg mx-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 py-4 w-full">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
          <p>&copy; 2024 Hostel XO. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p>Designed with <span class="text-yellow-500">&hearts;</span> by Hostel XO.</p>
